    Direct Known Subclasses:
    MockEditingContext, TemporaryEditingContext

    public abstract class AbstractEditingContextRule
extends er.extensions.eof.ERXEC
implements org.junit.rules.MethodRule
    AbstractEditingContextRule is a subclass of ERXEC that implements the MethodRule interface. This class provides the required infrastructure to properly initialize/dispose the ERXEC before/after the test execution.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Henrique Prange
